#
Decay B+sig
  1.000     MyJpsi          K+                 SVS; 
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig
#
Decay MyJpsi
  0.500     p+  MyantiSigma    K-  PHSP;
  0.500     anti-p-  MySigma    K+  PHSP;
Enddecay
#
Decay MySigma
1.0000    gamma  MyLambda                     PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay MyantiSigma
#
Decay MyLambda
  1.000     p+           pi-                HELAMP 0.9276 0.0 0.3735 0.0;
Enddecay
CDecay MyantiLambda
